text: The Oberbank Hungary is a commercial bank in Hungary, operating as the Hungarian subsidiary of austrian Oberbank AG, which is based in Linz and was founded in 1869. It has been active in Hungary since 2007. It currently has thirteen bank branches in Hungary: three in Budapest, and others in Debrecen, Győr, Kecskemét, Szeged, Nagykanizsa, Miskolc, Székesfehérvár, Tatabánya, Pécs and Szombathely. ==References== Category:Banks of Hungary
title: Oberbank Hungary
